article.description: — Kris Wooten came off the bench to knock down 6 of 7 3-point attempts and his 18 points helped spark Elon to a 107-62 romp past Division III Randolph College on Friday night.
article.headline: Wooten's 18 spark Elon's rout of D-III Randolph, 107-62
article.linkText: Wooten's 18 spark Elon's rout of D-III Randolph, 107-62
article.story: ELON, N.C. -- — Kris Wooten came off the bench to knock down 6 of 7 3-point attempts and his 18 points helped spark Elon to a 107-62 romp past Division III Randolph College on Friday night. Zac Ervin, Hunter McIntosh, Torrence Watson and Hunter Woods each scored 15 points for the Phoenix (1-1). Michael Graham pulled down 10 rebounds. Jordan Phillips-McLoyd scored 22 points to lead the Wildcats. ------
